==現況==
教區包括[[卡塞塔省|卡塞塔省]]東北部共廿四市，教座位於[[阿利費|阿利費]]。2012年有教友69,572人，佔轄區總人口99.4%。教區下轄四十四個堂區，有五十六名司鐸。

教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]，[[宗座署理|宗座署理]]為{{link-it|奧拉齊奧·方濟各·皮亞扎|Orazio Francesco Piazza}}，榮休主教為{{link-it|華倫泰·迪塞波|Valentino Di Cerbo}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 30.04.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/04/30/190430a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809184616/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/04/30/190430a.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=en |date=2019-04-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

